1
00:00:43,060 --> 00:00:46,780
=Auspicious Nobles=

2
00:00:47,580 --> 00:00:49,940
=Episode 5=

3
00:00:49,940 --> 00:00:52,500
(You're Really the Second Prince)

4
00:00:53,220 --> 00:00:55,860
(Uphold the Law with Justice)

5
00:00:58,920 --> 00:00:59,520
Your Highness.

6
00:01:00,150 --> 00:01:02,400
We've investigated the heads of all
six imperial merchant families.

7
00:01:02,420 --> 00:01:03,430
Some of their businesses

8
00:01:03,430 --> 00:01:04,830
were all supplied by the Second Prince.

9
00:01:04,840 --> 00:01:06,330
Only one family is a little different.

10
00:01:06,590 --> 00:01:07,230
Who?

11
00:01:07,260 --> 00:01:08,510
The Li family in the eastern district.

12
00:01:08,510 --> 00:01:09,590
(Inventory of the Li Family
in the Eastern District)

13
00:01:09,590 --> 00:01:11,120
Although their shops aren't very large,

14
00:01:11,590 --> 00:01:12,230
they sell

15
00:01:12,590 --> 00:01:14,070
(Information on the Second Prince's Imperial Merchants)
all kinds of unusual goods.

16
00:01:14,390 --> 00:01:15,710
It has the feel of Wangshi Tower.

17
00:01:15,710 --> 00:01:17,950
This nail polish and nail art

18
00:01:18,310 --> 00:01:20,920
really do have the Tower Master's touch.

19
00:01:23,120 --> 00:01:24,830
Who's in charge
of the Li family's business?

20
00:01:24,840 --> 00:01:25,760
Li Qingqing.

21
00:01:30,560 --> 00:01:32,040
Li Qingqing.

22
00:01:34,380 --> 00:01:37,740
(Zhao)

23
00:01:38,920 --> 00:01:39,350
This...

24
00:01:42,400 --> 00:01:43,120
Yang.

25
00:01:43,280 --> 00:01:44,920
Could there be some misunderstanding?

26
00:01:45,230 --> 00:01:47,680
How could Qingqing
be involved with another man?

27
00:01:48,710 --> 00:01:49,350
See?

28
00:01:50,150 --> 00:01:51,790
The beauty understands me after all.

29
00:01:54,120 --> 00:01:55,230
Mother,

30
00:01:55,560 --> 00:01:57,950
Qingqing has always been out
managing the family's business.

31
00:01:58,040 --> 00:02:01,200
It's only natural
that she spends time around men.

32
00:02:01,640 --> 00:02:03,040
Perhaps...

33
00:02:03,350 --> 00:02:05,510
Perhaps she was seduced
by that scoundrel

34
00:02:05,760 --> 00:02:07,310
and lost her way for a moment.

35
00:02:08,520 --> 00:02:10,310
You think everyone's like you,

36
00:02:10,630 --> 00:02:12,470
throwing yourself at any man you see?

37
00:02:12,800 --> 00:02:14,150
- Stop talking nonsense.
- You...

38
00:02:15,560 --> 00:02:17,630
How could Muyan ever be compared to you?

39
00:02:17,840 --> 00:02:19,590
I have nothing to do with him.

40
00:02:19,910 --> 00:02:21,080
But even if I did,

41
00:02:21,290 --> 00:02:22,710
you can go find yourself another woman.

42
00:02:22,710 --> 00:02:23,990
I'll put a green hat on you too.

43
00:02:24,150 --> 00:02:25,150
Fair's fair.

44
00:02:25,310 --> 00:02:26,000
Enough!

45
00:02:26,730 --> 00:02:29,420
Since ancient times, men have been
allowed multiple wives and concubines.

46
00:02:29,430 --> 00:02:31,190
How can a woman have two husbands?

47
00:02:31,800 --> 00:02:32,840
What a shameless woman.

48
00:02:33,000 --> 00:02:33,750
How old-fashioned.

49
00:02:34,360 --> 00:02:35,000
General!

50
00:02:36,150 --> 00:02:36,680
General!

51
00:02:36,780 --> 00:02:38,520
There's a good-looking
pretty boy outside.

52
00:02:38,520 --> 00:02:39,280
He looks furious.

53
00:02:39,280 --> 00:02:40,790
He says he's here
to see the Young Madam.

54
00:02:45,800 --> 00:02:48,000
Another pretty boy?

55
00:02:49,400 --> 00:02:50,310
Li Qingqing.

56
00:02:50,910 --> 00:02:52,190
You've really got some nerve.

57
00:02:52,360 --> 00:02:54,150
You've got more than one lover.

58
00:02:56,150 --> 00:02:57,000
How brazen.

59
00:02:57,520 --> 00:02:58,310
Absolutely brazen.

60
00:03:00,030 --> 00:03:01,190
Let's see how you'll explain yourself

61
00:03:02,560 --> 00:03:03,150
this time.

62
00:03:03,150 --> 00:03:04,400
Just hear what he has to say.

63
00:03:04,400 --> 00:03:05,520
Don't be rash.

64
00:03:05,680 --> 00:03:06,560
Who is Li Qingqing?

65
00:03:06,560 --> 00:03:08,230
Well, you've certainly
been getting around.

66
00:03:08,240 --> 00:03:09,000
They just keep showing up
one after another.

67
00:03:09,000 --> 00:03:10,630
Do you really think I'm dead?

68
00:03:12,470 --> 00:03:13,000
How dare you!

69
00:03:13,570 --> 00:03:15,390
How dare you show
such disrespect to the Crown Prince!

70
00:03:15,470 --> 00:03:16,360
The Crown Prince?

71
00:03:22,000 --> 00:03:23,560
(What's that scheming fool doing here?)

72
00:03:23,570 --> 00:03:25,490
(Could he have found out
who I am and come to kill me?)

73
00:03:28,840 --> 00:03:29,400
Pah!

74
00:03:30,310 --> 00:03:32,240
First someone claimed
to be the Second Prince,

75
00:03:32,240 --> 00:03:33,990
and now someone's
claiming to be the Crown Prince.

76
00:03:34,310 --> 00:03:36,680
You shameless woman.

77
00:03:37,020 --> 00:03:39,660
Do you really think you could win
the favor of an imperial prince?

78
00:03:42,750 --> 00:03:43,430
You brat.

79
00:03:44,080 --> 00:03:46,800
You've got some nerve pretending
to be the Crown Prince.

80
00:03:47,910 --> 00:03:49,150
Have you got a death wish?

81
00:03:49,840 --> 00:03:51,800
Take a good look at yourself.

82
00:03:52,230 --> 00:03:54,630
You think putting on a stern face
makes you the Crown Prince?

83
00:03:55,000 --> 00:03:56,960
Why not claim to be
the King of Hell while you're at it?

84
00:03:58,710 --> 00:04:00,150
If you don't want your tongue,

85
00:04:01,560 --> 00:04:03,240
I'll cut it out for you.

86
00:04:04,680 --> 00:04:05,520
(That voice...)

87
00:04:07,030 --> 00:04:08,280
Lighten my burden?

88
00:04:09,590 --> 00:04:10,960
Do you think you're qualified?

89
00:04:20,480 --> 00:04:21,830
It seems, General Pan,

90
00:04:22,630 --> 00:04:24,000
your tongue isn't much use.

91
00:04:25,480 --> 00:04:27,630
Your hearing isn't much better either.

92
00:04:29,500 --> 00:04:29,870
Perhaps...

93
00:04:29,870 --> 00:04:30,460
Your Highness!

94
00:04:30,600 --> 00:04:31,630
Your Highness, spare me!

95
00:04:31,630 --> 00:04:32,220
Your Highness!

96
00:04:32,310 --> 00:04:33,040
The Crown Prince?

97
00:04:33,050 --> 00:04:34,220
It really is the Crown Prince.

98
00:04:35,210 --> 00:04:37,430
- Greetings, Your Highness.
- Greetings, Your Highness.

99
00:04:39,920 --> 00:04:40,680
Your Highness,

100
00:04:41,120 --> 00:04:43,070
I...

101
00:04:43,400 --> 00:04:44,680
I mistook you for someone else.

102
00:04:44,920 --> 00:04:47,750
I beg Your Highness
to forgive my offense.

103
00:04:49,270 --> 00:04:51,630
- Spare us, Your Highness.
- Spare us, Your Highness.

104
00:04:56,800 --> 00:04:58,040
Who is Li Qingqing?

105
00:05:01,830 --> 00:05:02,630
Your Highness

106
00:05:02,630 --> 00:05:04,310
wishes to summon Li Qingqing.

107
00:05:05,190 --> 00:05:05,920
Li Qingqing!

108
00:05:06,120 --> 00:05:07,980
Why don't you come out
and pay your respects to His Highness?

109
00:05:09,190 --> 00:05:09,680
Hurry!

110
00:05:30,870 --> 00:05:31,630
(It's her.)

111
00:05:36,270 --> 00:05:37,480
(So last time...)

112
00:05:38,240 --> 00:05:39,720
(I wasn't mistaken after all.)

113
00:05:42,070 --> 00:05:42,590
Hurry!

114
00:05:42,590 --> 00:05:45,970
♪Your dark hair
brushes across my fingertips♪

115
00:05:46,290 --> 00:05:47,070
(It's just that...)

116
00:05:48,190 --> 00:05:49,750
(She's already married.)

117
00:05:52,040 --> 00:05:52,750
Kneel.

118
00:05:54,480 --> 00:05:56,510
Greetings, Your Highness.

119
00:05:57,510 --> 00:05:58,430
Rise and answer me.

120
00:05:59,310 --> 00:06:00,630
Thank you, Your Highness.

121
00:06:03,470 --> 00:06:05,390
♪Though fate tries♪

122
00:06:05,390 --> 00:06:07,970
♪To make us pass each other by♪

123
00:06:08,190 --> 00:06:11,610
♪I choose to make our story whole♪

124
00:06:11,870 --> 00:06:13,500
♪Though time slips by♪

125
00:06:13,500 --> 00:06:15,260
♪As day turns into night♪

126
00:06:17,480 --> 00:06:18,560
You don't remember me?

127
00:06:21,480 --> 00:06:22,240
(I'm done for.)

128
00:06:22,630 --> 00:06:24,680
(He's definitely here to test me.)

129
00:06:25,650 --> 00:06:27,220
The Inspectorate
is conducting an investigation.

130
00:06:27,390 --> 00:06:27,920
Li Qingqing.

131
00:06:28,240 --> 00:06:29,920
Answer whatever His Highness asks you.

132
00:06:33,630 --> 00:06:34,800
The... The Inspectorate?

133
00:06:35,310 --> 00:06:36,070
Your Highness.

134
00:06:36,800 --> 00:06:39,000
Although Li Qingqing is my wife,

135
00:06:39,000 --> 00:06:41,480
what she does outside the house
is beyond my knowledge.

136
00:06:42,120 --> 00:06:43,480
You shameless woman, kneel!

137
00:06:43,480 --> 00:06:44,270
Kneel!

138
00:06:44,720 --> 00:06:45,360
Now...

139
00:06:52,870 --> 00:06:53,830
Miss Qingqing.

140
00:06:54,920 --> 00:06:56,480
While running your business,

141
00:06:56,680 --> 00:06:58,870
have you ever worked with Wangshi Tower?

142
00:07:02,190 --> 00:07:03,680
Wangshi Tower?

143
00:07:04,600 --> 00:07:06,120
I wish I had.

144
00:07:07,120 --> 00:07:09,040
Does Your Highness have any connections?

145
00:07:09,090 --> 00:07:11,300
If Your Highness could put me
in touch with Wangshi Tower,

146
00:07:11,310 --> 00:07:14,310
I'm willing to give
Your Highness twenty percent...

147
00:07:16,040 --> 00:07:17,390
Fifteen percent of the profits.

148
00:07:17,390 --> 00:07:18,510
Have you lost your mind?

149
00:07:18,700 --> 00:07:21,170
Do you think His Highness
would care about your little share?

150
00:07:23,010 --> 00:07:24,310
I'm the one asking the questions.

151
00:07:24,870 --> 00:07:26,630
Did I give you permission to speak?

152
00:07:38,510 --> 00:07:39,390
Tell me,

153
00:07:40,700 --> 00:07:42,950
have you truly never had
any dealings with Wangshi Tower?

154
00:07:49,120 --> 00:07:50,240
(Please, Heaven.)

155
00:07:50,430 --> 00:07:51,600
(If I can get through this,)

156
00:07:51,600 --> 00:07:53,790
(I'll donate hundreds of thousands
in incense offerings.)

157
00:07:54,040 --> 00:07:55,680
(Please, Heaven.)

158
00:07:56,480 --> 00:07:57,270
Let's go.

159
00:08:06,210 --> 00:08:08,970
(That scheming fool is like a mad dog
that catches the scent of meat.)

160
00:08:09,000 --> 00:08:10,190
(Once he sinks
his teeth into something,)

161
00:08:10,240 --> 00:08:11,800
(he won't let go without taking a bite.)

162
00:08:12,310 --> 00:08:14,480
(And yet today,
he's actually leaving just like that?)

163
00:08:14,480 --> 00:08:15,240
Your Highness.

164
00:08:15,520 --> 00:08:17,190
We're not going
to investigate Li Qingqing?

165
00:08:17,270 --> 00:08:18,160
We're just leaving?

166
00:08:18,220 --> 00:08:21,380
(Pan Residence)

167
00:08:24,540 --> 00:08:26,140
(Pan Residence)

168
00:08:37,390 --> 00:08:40,780
♪Snowflakes settle gently
upon your brows♪

169
00:08:41,540 --> 00:08:44,920
♪Your dark hair
brushes across my fingertips♪

170
00:08:45,690 --> 00:08:46,890
♪Your smile♪

171
00:08:46,910 --> 00:08:49,320
Handsome, be careful.
The road is slippery.

172
00:08:50,030 --> 00:08:51,200
After him! He's injured.

173
00:08:51,200 --> 00:08:52,080
He won't get far.

174
00:08:54,120 --> 00:08:57,430
♪Yet I stand before you♪

175
00:08:58,170 --> 00:09:02,000
♪Unable to recognize your eyes♪

176
00:09:02,420 --> 00:09:03,980
♪Though fate tries♪

177
00:09:04,000 --> 00:09:06,120
My dear, I'm so cold.

178
00:09:07,140 --> 00:09:10,560
♪I choose to make our story whole♪

179
00:09:10,820 --> 00:09:12,450
♪Though time slips by♪

180
00:09:12,450 --> 00:09:14,210
♪As day turns into night♪

181
00:09:15,240 --> 00:09:17,000
I thought I'd have to spend

182
00:09:17,000 --> 00:09:18,790
the Lantern Festival all alone tonight.

183
00:09:19,250 --> 00:09:21,530
I never thought I'd get to rescue
a handsome guy for once.

184
00:09:21,550 --> 00:09:23,340
♪Blessed by fate♪

185
00:09:23,340 --> 00:09:26,820
♪I believe this moment
will last forever♪

186
00:09:26,840 --> 00:09:28,720
Press this against the wound.
It'll help stop the bleeding.

187
00:09:28,720 --> 00:09:30,120
You should see a doctor right away.

188
00:09:30,430 --> 00:09:31,270
No need to thank me.

189
00:09:31,280 --> 00:09:33,780
♪Is the most beautiful poem♪

190
00:09:33,780 --> 00:09:37,400
♪I'd rather spend my days with you♪

191
00:09:37,920 --> 00:09:41,380
♪And wander the world together♪

192
00:09:41,380 --> 00:09:42,720
♪Holding you close♪

193
00:09:42,720 --> 00:09:45,260
♪Envying neither lovers nor immortals♪

194
00:09:45,260 --> 00:09:47,580
♪Your tenderness♪

195
00:09:47,580 --> 00:09:50,440
♪Is the brightest moon♪

196
00:09:50,440 --> 00:09:53,260
♪I'd rather
pledge three lifetimes to you♪

197
00:09:53,260 --> 00:09:55,740
(Crossbow)

198
00:09:55,750 --> 00:09:57,790
(What an ingenious crossbow design.)

199
00:09:58,960 --> 00:10:00,360
(Who is she?)

200
00:10:00,940 --> 00:10:05,190
♪My heart will remain forever pure♪

201
00:10:06,090 --> 00:10:08,250
♪Your smiling face♪

202
00:10:08,840 --> 00:10:09,390
Your Highness.

203
00:10:10,000 --> 00:10:11,300
The assassins have all been dealt with.

204
00:10:11,330 --> 00:10:15,200
♪I'd rather spend my days with you♪

205
00:10:16,350 --> 00:10:17,960
What are you looking for, Your Highness?

206
00:10:18,920 --> 00:10:20,240
♪Holding you close♪

207
00:10:20,240 --> 00:10:22,870
♪Envying neither lovers nor immortals♪

208
00:10:22,870 --> 00:10:25,130
♪Your tenderness♪

209
00:10:25,130 --> 00:10:28,000
♪Is the brightest moon♪

210
00:10:28,000 --> 00:10:31,740
♪I'd rather
pledge three lifetimes to you♪

211
00:10:32,180 --> 00:10:34,990
♪Our love will never fade away♪

212
00:10:35,000 --> 00:10:36,100
She's not the Tower Master.

213
00:10:36,400 --> 00:10:37,960
The Tower Master is far too calculating.

214
00:10:39,600 --> 00:10:40,960
She's nothing like her...

215
00:10:43,350 --> 00:10:44,480
She's far too kindhearted.

216
00:10:44,790 --> 00:10:46,510
How can Your Highness be so certain?

217
00:10:48,030 --> 00:10:49,240
What should we do next?

218
00:10:52,150 --> 00:10:53,750
Keep a close watch on the Second Prince.

219
00:10:54,280 --> 00:10:55,870
The Tower Master
will surely reveal herself.

220
00:10:58,080 --> 00:10:59,480
When the time comes, kill her.

221
00:11:02,390 --> 00:11:04,000
No matter how capable she may be,

222
00:11:05,550 --> 00:11:06,790
if she brings me no prosperity,

223
00:11:08,720 --> 00:11:09,750
she dies.

224
00:11:10,080 --> 00:11:10,630
Yes.

225
00:11:13,080 --> 00:11:13,910
Li Qingqing!

226
00:11:13,960 --> 00:11:14,790
What are you doing?

227
00:11:14,790 --> 00:11:15,870
Have you lost your mind?

228
00:11:16,000 --> 00:11:17,550
Do you have any idea what you've done?

229
00:11:18,000 --> 00:11:20,430
You actually dared to discuss business
with the Crown Prince.

230
00:11:20,440 --> 00:11:22,440
And you even wanted
to work with Wangshi Tower.

231
00:11:22,630 --> 00:11:23,790
Exactly, Qingqing.

232
00:11:24,080 --> 00:11:25,870
Judging by His Highness' expression,

233
00:11:26,080 --> 00:11:27,200
he must think

234
00:11:27,240 --> 00:11:28,840
we all feel the same way you do.

235
00:11:29,000 --> 00:11:31,080
You've directly
offended the Crown Prince.

236
00:11:31,480 --> 00:11:32,360
I'll teach you...

237
00:11:32,510 --> 00:11:34,000
What are you trying to do?

238
00:11:35,150 --> 00:11:35,550
You...

239
00:11:36,720 --> 00:11:37,790
He's trying to assault me!

240
00:11:37,790 --> 00:11:38,480
You...

241
00:11:38,870 --> 00:11:40,670
I think you should
get your head examined.

242
00:11:42,200 --> 00:11:43,030
You shrew!

243
00:11:45,080 --> 00:11:47,200
Qingqing has gone too far.

244
00:11:47,200 --> 00:11:49,440
How could she humiliate you like this?

245
00:11:51,000 --> 00:11:52,510
I'm going to find that lover of yours.

246
00:11:52,840 --> 00:11:54,870
Once he confesses,
I'll have you thrown into a pig cage.

247
00:11:57,750 --> 00:11:58,670
You fool!

248
00:11:59,030 --> 00:12:00,150
How dare you strike me!

249
00:12:00,410 --> 00:12:01,870
Just wait. I'll make you pay for this!

250
00:12:05,150 --> 00:12:05,630
Pan Yang!

251
00:12:06,030 --> 00:12:06,900
Have you got a death wish?

252
00:12:06,910 --> 00:12:07,550
Let go of me!

253
00:12:10,240 --> 00:12:11,870
You reckless fool!

254
00:12:12,360 --> 00:12:14,000
I'll have your entire clan executed!

255
00:12:14,360 --> 00:12:16,910
How long have you
been carrying on with Li Qingqing?

256
00:12:17,870 --> 00:12:18,670
And this...

257
00:12:20,200 --> 00:12:21,030
Is this

258
00:12:21,320 --> 00:12:23,360
your token of love?

259
00:12:23,360 --> 00:12:24,080
(Zhao)

260
00:12:24,080 --> 00:12:24,960
You fool.

261
00:12:25,440 --> 00:12:27,510
Open your eyes and take a good look.

262
00:12:27,840 --> 00:12:29,550
What's the character
on this jade pendant?

263
00:12:32,480 --> 00:12:33,270
Zhao.

264
00:12:34,200 --> 00:12:35,270
Then tell me,

265
00:12:35,960 --> 00:12:38,750
what is the Second Prince's given name?

266
00:12:39,630 --> 00:12:41,630
Still pretending
to be the Second Prince?

267
00:12:41,870 --> 00:12:44,270
Dressed like that,

268
00:12:44,270 --> 00:12:47,150
you don't have the slightest trace
of imperial dignity.

269
00:12:47,360 --> 00:12:48,870
At best, you're nothing
but a useless drunk

270
00:12:48,870 --> 00:12:50,510
from a pleasure house.

271
00:12:50,510 --> 00:12:53,200
And Li Qingqing, she's nothing more
than a vulgar merchant.

272
00:12:53,200 --> 00:12:54,540
I wouldn't even spare her a glance.

273
00:12:54,550 --> 00:12:55,080
Pan Yang.

274
00:12:55,080 --> 00:12:57,350
Do you really think a prince
of the imperial family would?

275
00:12:57,750 --> 00:12:59,510
Keep talking.

276
00:12:59,750 --> 00:13:01,240
We'll see

277
00:13:01,240 --> 00:13:03,550
how long you can keep acting tough.

278
00:13:05,960 --> 00:13:06,720
Pan Yang!

279
00:13:09,750 --> 00:13:10,550
Your Highness!

280
00:13:25,270 --> 00:13:27,320
It... It really is the Second Prince.

281
00:13:27,550 --> 00:13:28,510
You...

282
00:13:29,030 --> 00:13:30,600
You're as good as dead.

283
00:13:36,630 --> 00:13:40,020
♪Snowflakes settle gently
upon your brows♪

284
00:13:40,780 --> 00:13:44,160
♪Your dark hair
brushes across my fingertips♪

285
00:13:44,930 --> 00:13:46,670
♪Your smile♪

286
00:13:46,930 --> 00:13:49,220
♪Melts away the winter snow♪

287
00:13:49,220 --> 00:13:52,900
♪One fleeting glance says more
than a thousand words♪

288
00:13:53,360 --> 00:13:56,670
♪Yet I stand before you♪

289
00:13:57,410 --> 00:14:01,240
♪Unable to recognize your eyes♪

290
00:14:01,660 --> 00:14:03,580
♪Though fate tries♪

291
00:14:03,580 --> 00:14:06,160
♪To make us pass each other by♪

292
00:14:06,380 --> 00:14:09,800
♪I choose to make our story whole♪

293
00:14:10,060 --> 00:14:11,690
♪Though time slips by♪

294
00:14:11,690 --> 00:14:13,450
♪As day turns into night♪

295
00:14:13,970 --> 00:14:17,990
♪I still remember
our days at Wangshi Tower♪

296
00:14:18,410 --> 00:14:20,790
♪One glance at you lasts a lifetime♪

297
00:14:20,790 --> 00:14:22,580
♪Blessed by fate♪

298
00:14:22,580 --> 00:14:27,740
♪I believe this moment
will last forever♪

299
00:14:27,740 --> 00:14:30,180
♪Your smiling face♪

300
00:14:30,180 --> 00:14:33,020
♪Is the most beautiful poem♪

301
00:14:33,020 --> 00:14:36,640
♪I'd rather spend my days with you♪

302
00:14:37,160 --> 00:14:40,620
♪And wander the world together♪

303
00:14:40,620 --> 00:14:41,960
♪Holding you close♪

304
00:14:41,960 --> 00:14:44,500
♪Envying neither lovers nor immortals♪

305
00:14:44,500 --> 00:14:46,820
♪Your tenderness♪

306
00:14:46,820 --> 00:14:49,680
♪Is the brightest moon♪

307
00:14:49,680 --> 00:14:53,380
♪I'd rather
pledge three lifetimes to you♪

308
00:14:53,900 --> 00:14:57,190
♪Our love will never fade away♪

309
00:14:57,190 --> 00:14:59,650
♪Though heaven and earth grow old♪

310
00:15:00,180 --> 00:15:04,430
♪My heart will remain forever pure♪

